{{Youmay| the [[Nuiwit]] Council of Elders| other groups called the [[Elders (disambiguation)|Council of Elders]]|linebreak=1}}
The [[Nuiwit]] people of [[Altor 14]] were governed by several co-operating '''Councils of Elders'''. The name was somewhat inaccurate, as age was not the primary qualification for membership. True to the pacifist, non-confrontational nature of the Nuiwit people, the Councils of Elders reached decisions via consensus.

